flowchart TD
    Resp[Full LLM response text] --> Strip[strip_citation_markers<br/>before TTS and display]
    Resp --> Should{should_attach_citations}

    Should -->|conversational intent| Skip[No citations sent]
    Should -->|insufficient answer patterns| Skip
    Should -->|response length lt 10| Skip
    Should -->|no chunk pool| Skip
    Should -->|pass| Filter[filter_relevant_chunks]

    Filter --> Sort[Sort top 8 by rerank_score<br/>take top 5]
    Sort --> Loc{location query}
    Loc -->|yes| DropCase[Drop case_studies titles]
    Loc -->|no| Score
    DropCase --> Score

    Score{Per chunk score}
    Score -->|rerank_score gte 2.0| Keep[Keep chunk]
    Score -->|weak score gte -8.0<br/>AND answer term overlap gte 3| Keep
    Score -->|else| Drop[Drop chunk]

    Keep --> Topic[_prefer_topic_documents]
    Topic --> Dedupe[_dedupe_documents max 3 titles]
    Dedupe --> Empty{Any selected?}

    Empty -->|no| Fallback[Fallback dedupe from context_chunks]
    Empty -->|yes| Payload[build_citation_payload]
    Fallback --> Payload

    Payload --> WS[WebSocket type citations<br/>id document_id title text<br/>section line_start line_end rerank_score]
